        "configMap"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我把Developer放在中间位置，向上连接FinTech_PaymentGateway，向下分出两条线到Infrastructure和configMap，同时Infrastructure和configMap之间也建立关联。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Developer",
